  <title>Shepherdstown Community Club</title>
  <abstract>This dataset contains attributes about the Ash Tree Inventory at Morgan's Grove Park owned by Shepherdstown Community Club and operated by Jefferson County. 

Park Director: Carrie Blessing
Data Collection: Carrie Blessing
Data Processing: Rachel Pierce

This dataset is intended for use in a web map application enabling users to select and adopt/sponsor a tree through the web application.
Data was recorded using a Garmin hand held GPS unit.
CRS: WGS84
Units: HDDD.mm.mmm (DEGREES MINUTES MINUTES) and was converted to DECIMAL DEGREES.

</abstract>
